# Learnings Tracker -- {{ project_name }}

This file aggregates learnings from retrospectives for periodic review and incorporation into guardrails.

## How This Works

Retrospectives capture lessons learned after plan execution. Learnings are extracted here for periodic review. Incorporate them into AGENTS.md, templates, standards, or prompts to improve future execution.

Flow: Plan Execution -> Retrospective -> Learnings extracted -> Periodic Review -> Incorporation into guardrails

## Commands

```bash
# Check for missing retrospectives
scaffold retro check

# Extract learnings for review
scaffold retro check --extract

# Fail if retrospectives missing (for CI)
scaffold retro check --warn
```

